data.description: Great investment opportunity to purchase this partially renovated home in the only community on Pine Island with a county park that has its own beach and boat launch that intersects with The Great Calusa Blueway Paddling Trail, a 190-mile marked canoe and kayak trail that meanders through the coastal and inland waters of Lee County. Tropical Homesites is a friendly, walkable community, with newer homes, paved roads, no HOA, and city water. This 3-bedroom + den, 2-bath, 2-car garage was built in 2020 and although sustained some damage from Hurricane Ian, a NEW METAL ROOF has been installed as well as drywall removal, paint, stucco and other repairs. Some of the home's features include a paver driveway and entryway, stone columns, color-matching soffit, fascia and gutters, and ceramic tile flooring. Most of the remediation work has been completed. Home is being sold As-Is.
